       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. SSHFling-Consumer.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-EXPECTED PIC X(32).
       01  WS-VERSION PIC X(32).
       01  WS-ARGUMENT-COUNT PIC 9(9) COMP-5 VALUE 1.
       01  WS-ARGUMENT-BUFFER PIC X(32) VALUE LOW-VALUES.
       01  WS-STATUS PIC S9(9) COMP-5 VALUE 0.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           DISPLAY 1 UPON ARGUMENT-NUMBER
           END-DISPLAY
           ACCEPT WS-EXPECTED FROM ARGUMENT-VALUE
           END-ACCEPT
           CALL "SSHFling-Version" USING BY REFERENCE WS-VERSION
           END-CALL
           IF FUNCTION TRIM(WS-VERSION) NOT = FUNCTION TRIM(WS-EXPECTED)
               MOVE 1 TO RETURN-CODE
               GOBACK
           END-IF
           MOVE "--version" TO WS-ARGUMENT-BUFFER
           MOVE LOW-VALUE TO WS-ARGUMENT-BUFFER(10:1)
           CALL "SSHFling-Run" USING
               BY VALUE WS-ARGUMENT-COUNT
               BY REFERENCE WS-ARGUMENT-BUFFER
               BY REFERENCE WS-STATUS
           END-CALL
           MOVE WS-STATUS TO RETURN-CODE
           GOBACK.
       END PROGRAM SSHFling-Consumer.
